The paper specifically focuses on the use of deep learning models for NER, which suggests that it is likely to fall under the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of supervised and semi-supervised learning algorithms, which are common in Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of NER in information retrieval (IR), which is another sub-category of Computer Science.
